playstore_details.title: VietinBank OTP
playstore_details.description:
VietinBank OTP application exclusively for VietinBank Corporate Customers.
VietinBank OTP is an advanced authentication solution with the highest level of security developed by Vietnam Joint Stock Commercial Bank for Industry and Trade and the leading security partners. VietinBank OTP is installed on mobile devices to get one-time password (OTP) code when customers make transactions on online banking service VietinBank eFAST. 
As the advanced authentication method exclusively for Corporate Customers, VietinBank OTP will definitely bring customers a completely satisfied experience with the following outstanding features:
-	Authenticate modern security system
-	Confirm all transactions by remember 6 numbers of VietinBank OTP code without hard-token
-	Obligatory for all domestic and international money transfer transactions. Stable and usable even when there are - no phone waves and Internet functions
-	Easy Registers
-	Unlimited users within the application.
-	Comply with the State Bank of Việt Nam’s regulations on D- transactions (document no. 630/QĐ-NHNN).

To register for VietinBank OTP, please contact VietinBank Branch/Transaction office nationwide to be served.
For further information, please contact VietinBank Contact Center: Hotline 1900 558 868 Email: contact@vietinbank.vn or website: https://www.vietinbank.vn.
